# --- Dependencies (reinstalled fresh in the image anyway) ---
**/node_modules

# --- Build outputs (client build happens INSIDE the Docker build stage) ---
**/build
**/dist

# --- Environment & secrets (never bake these into an image) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Git ---
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# --- Logs ---
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/*.log

# --- Editor/OS junk ---
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# --- Docker-related files (no need to copy these into the image) ---
.dockerignore

# --- Test & coverage output ---
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# --- Misc ---
**/*.md
**/tmp
**/.cache